media-camel

Python and Ruby scripts to rename media files.

Scripts will get rid of spaces in filenames of ogg and mp3 files,
and Camel Case things.

Before: Various-Wonderful world sam cooke.ogg
After: VariousWonderfulWorldSamCooke.ogg

Before: Various-20th century boy t rex.ogg
After: Various20thCenturyBoytRex.ogg

ls *.ogg | ruby camel_case_no_space.rb
ls *.ogg | ruby camel_case_no_space.rb 'mv' 'max'
find . -type f -name '*.ogg' | ruby camel_case_no_space.rb 'mv' 'max'

See included LICENSE file (GPL) regarding media-camel being free software.
